Enum E_ConfigKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<E_ConfigKey>
      • de.fraunhofer.fokus.oefit.adhoc.custom.E_ConfigKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<E_ConfigKey>

    public enum E_ConfigKey
extends Enum<E_ConfigKey>
    An enum describing available configuration keys, their default value and (if available) their link/id to global portal settings
